"Summing up, MMZ can or cannot be classified as MM - she can be both 'grandmother' and 'paternal aunt'. A MM, however, will never be classified as a paternal aunt, even if she is. In other words, lineal kin does not 'fold up' to avuncular obliquity. Nevertheless, every collateral step is a move away from dravidian logic—a MM is always a 'grandmother', a MMZ is not always a 'grandmother' and a classificatory sister is never a 'grandmother'."
